# UI Sections Builder Guide

**Figma:** [UI Sections](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=348-13000&p=f&m=dev)

Section types and component mappings below are derived from Figma node 348:13000. Load only the component rules you need.

---

## Section type → Component rules

| Section type | Load | Key components |
|--------------|------|-----------------|
| **Forms** | ds-input, ds-selection, ds-button | Inputs, radio, checkbox, toggle, dropdown, date picker; Cancel + Save |
| **Data lists / tables** | ds-lists, ds-button, ds-dropdown | Search, Add New, Sort, Filter; rows with checkbox, data, actions |
| **Cards grid** | ds-card, ds-button | Product, pricing, testimonial cards; image + title + description + CTA |
| **Empty state** | ds-button | Title, descriptive text, icon placeholder, primary action |
| **Activity feed / timeline** | ds-avatar, ds-lists | Avatar, title, timestamp, description; Read/Unread status |
| **Notifications area** | ds-notifications | With CTA, Without CTA; Type, Position; Light/Dark |
| **Modals / drawers** | ds-modal | Title, content, Cancel + Save; Close/Back in header |
| **Navigation sidebar** | ds-navbar | Vertical nav; active `--bg-brand-tertiary`; SECTION headers |
| **Tabs** | ds-navbar | Horizontal tabs; active teal underline or filled |
| **Profile / user cards** | ds-avatar, ds-card | Avatar, name, status |
| **Breadcrumbs** | ds-typography | Label 1 / Label 2 / Label 3 |
| **Pricing tiers** | ds-card, ds-button | Basic, Standard, Premium; feature lists; "Get Started" |

---

## Implementation cues

| Cue | Value |
|-----|-------|
| **Spacing** | Section gaps Space/600–1200; component Space/200–400; inline Space/100–200 |
| **Layout** | Grid for cards; vertical stack for lists; two-column for forms when space allows |
| **Colors** | Primary `--bg-brand-default`; surfaces `--bg-base-default`, `--bg-base-secondary`, `--bg-base-tertiary`; borders `--border-base-default`; semantic variants |
| **Responsiveness** | Breakpoints 375, 768, 1200 |
| **Tokens** | Use `var(--*)`; never hardcode. See `design-system-tokens.mdc` |

---

## Quick reference

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Primary action | `--bg-brand-default` button |
| Secondary action | Outlined or text button |
| Active/selected | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |
| Success | `--bg-success-default` |
| Error | `--bg-danger-default` |
| Warning | `--bg-warning-default` |
| Info | `--bg-brand-default` |

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Do not invent section types; implement only what exists in Figma node 348:13000.
